      "content": "REST surface of the DeepL Voice API used to request and reconnect a real-time voice transcription / translation session. The session metadata returned by these endpoints (streaming_url + token) is then used to establish a WebSocket connection described by the companion AsyncAPI specification.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: DeepL Developers",
